flowchart LR
  user((User))
  browser[Web Dashboard<br/>public/index.html]
  app[Node.js App<br/>Express + REST APIs]
  db[(MongoDB)]
  broker[(Mosquitto MQTT Broker)]
  esp[ESP32 Reminder Device]
  ntp[NTP Server]
  lan{{Local WiFi / LAN}}
  nodered[Node-RED<br/>Optional automation]
  flows[(node-red-flows.json)]

  user -->|Log in, register devices,
  create medicine schedules| browser
  browser <-->|HTTP UI + session auth| app
  app <-->|Read / write users,
  devices, medicines, intake| db

  app <-->|Publish / subscribe| broker
  esp <-->|MQTT schedule request,
  intake, heartbeat| broker
  broker -->|Schedule JSON| esp

  esp -->|Time sync| ntp
  esp --> lan
  lan --> app
  lan --> broker
  esp -->|HTTP fallback / compatibility| app

  nodered -->|Import| flows
  nodered <-->|MQTT / HTTP automation| broker
  nodered <-->|Optional admin flows| app

  app -->|Serve dashboard assets| browser
